<HEADLINE>
<P>
SEISMIC RULES ON CAMPUS GARAGES TIGHTENED; SAFETY: COLLAPSE OF CAL STATE 
NORTHRIDGE PARKING STRUCTURE SPURS CHANGES. BUILDINGS THROUGHOUT THE UNIVERSITY 
SYSTEM WILL BE REVIEWED. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOHN CHANDLER, TIMES STAFF WRITER 
</P>
