</P>
<P>
 * May 7, 3 p.m.: "The Dream" (Ashton, Mendelssohn): Benjamin, Carreno; "Tales 
of Beatrix Potter" (Ashton, John Lanchbery): to be announced. 
</P>
<P>
 * May 7, 8 p.m.: "The Dream": Collier, William Trevitt; "Tales": to be 
announced. 
</P>
<P>
 * May 8, 2 p.m.: "The Dream": Sarah Wildor, Tetsuya Kumakawa; "Tales": to be 
announced. 
</P>
<P>
 * May 8, 7:30 p.m.: "The Dream": Durante, Sansom; "Tales": to be announced. 
</P>
<P>
 Tickets for individual programs, ranging from $20 to $70, will go on sale 
Sunday. Information: (714) 556-2787. 
</P>
